Teacher Selection System

Originally the frontend attempted to fetch teachers from:

/api/users/?role=teacher

This produced:

404 Not Found

because no dedicated admin endpoint existed for teacher retrieval.

Solution

A dedicated Django application was created:

admin_dashboard

This app centralizes all admin-only APIs.

A new endpoint was added:

GET /api/admin-dashboard/teachers/

This endpoint returns only users with:

role = teacher

Benefits:

Cleaner architecture
Better separation
Avoid mixing admin logic into unrelated apps
Easier future scaling
