React Hook Optimization Problems

Several React Hook warnings appeared during development.

Example warnings:

react-hooks/exhaustive-deps
react-hooks/set-state-in-effect

These appeared in:

LessonsList.tsx
LessonResources.tsx

Cause:

Functions that updated state were being called directly inside:

useEffect()

without proper dependency handling.

Solution

The logic was refactored using:

let isMounted = true

and async loaders inside effects.

Benefits:

Prevented cascading renders
Prevented memory leaks
Fixed ESLint warnings
Improved React performance
