Video Upload Methods

Administrators can upload videos using:

1. Device Upload
Upload from Device

The browser uploads directly to Mux.

Flow:

Frontend
→ Django creates upload URL
→ Browser uploads directly to Mux
→ Mux processes video
→ Webhook updates lesson
2. URL Upload

Administrators can also upload videos using:

