Video Webhook System

Mux sends webhook events to Django.

Webhook URL:

/api/admin-dashboard/mux/webhook/

Webhook responsibilities:

Detect completed videos
Save playback IDs
Save asset IDs
Link videos to lessons automatically
Important Mux Event

The main event used:

video.asset.ready

This indicates:

Video processing completed successfully
Passthrough System

Each uploaded video includes:

passthrough = lesson_id

Example:

"passthrough": "3"

This allows Django to know which lesson the uploaded video belongs to.

Signed Playback Preparation

Playback IDs are generated using:

